<div class="card-body">
<h5 class="card-title"><a href="https://providencemag.com/2021/07/court-packing-hurts-independent-judges-citizens/" class="link-black">Court-Packing Hurts Independent Judges and Citizens</a></h5>
<p class="card-text"><a href="https://providencemag.com/authors/aaron-rhodes/">Aaron Rhodes</a><br /><small class="text-muted">July 7, 2021</small></p>
